en_561292_0	A sudden bush fire erupted in Divithotawela area in the Badulla district Tuesday (12) evening was brought under control by the troops of the Security Force Headquarters - Central (SFHQ-Cen) after the emergency was brought to the notice of the troops serving in the area.
en_561292_1	Commander, Security Forces - Central (SF-Cen), Major General Rukmal Dias on being informed of the emergency situation directed his troops to immediately rush to the area with the assistance of civil authorities in the area.
en_561292_2	The group of Army personnel including 1 Officer and 15 Other Rankers jumped into action and brought the fast spreading fire under control within hours.
en_561292_3	The reason for the outbreak of the fire is yet to be identified.
